lJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/S%E1%BB%9F-H%C3%A1n-chi%E1%BA%BFn-x%E1%BB%A9/poem-eCbDJxhsFiYjtI65mX63ww">Sở Hán chiến xứ - 楚漢戰處</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/S%C6%A1n-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-li%E1%BB%85u-T%E1%BA%B7ng-ca-n%E1%BB%AF/poem-NKrCsk62l0nMe6MkPHNZTg">Sơn đình liễu - Tặng ca nữ - 山亭柳－贈歌女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-Th%C3%B9/author-vOEpptlMHWVC0_k_NsTzRg">Án Thù</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-Hoan/poem-GTCNrO8KpMy-W-0WeDA4Zg">Thị tử Hoan - 示子懽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/Tri%E1%BB%87u-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-ca/poem-ewFKlhoPECIc4wyIoeEdGQ">Triệu tướng quân ca - 趙將軍歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br></div>	</div>
